data.description: PRICE PER SQ FT. ON SITE INFORMATION DOES NOT INCLUDE THE 700 SQUARE FOOT BONUS HOUSE. PRICE PER SQ FT IS ACTUALLY 158.94. Escape to the tranquility of rural living, while being only minutes from town, with this exquisite 3-acre property. A picturesque front porch welcomes you, offering breathtaking views. This spacious, approximately 2,420 sq. ft. home features 3 large bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms in the main house. Storage is never an issue here! From walk-in closets to a generously sized garage, you'll have ample space to organize your belongings and keep your home clutter-free. The primary bedroom is a retreat of its own, complete with an ensuite bathroom and ample closet space, ensuring privacy and convenience.  Additionally, a charming approximately 700 sq foot mother-in-law quarters or pool house with 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom, garage parking and a kitchenette awaits. Don't forget the adorable 12x16 storage building behind the pool house! Countless updates, including new air units, ensure your comfort. Don't miss this opportunity – come experience the rural charm for yourself!
